title: My Life Without Me
actors: Sarah Polley, Amanda Plummer, Scott Speedman, Leonor Watling
plot: Ann, 23 years old, lives a modest life with her two kids and her husband in a trailer in her mother's garden. Her life takes a dramatic turn, when her doctor tells her that she has uterine cancer and only two months to live. She compiles a list of things to do before she dies.
